https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sJAVATFswmDRnVa0wut05CRXC1B.jpg Hosted by Janeane Garafalo, this made-for-TV documentary treats animation fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of DARIA, the spin-off from BEAVIS AND BUTT-HEAD about an intelligent teenage girl surround by a world full of idiots. Features various interviews with the cast and crew of the series who share insights into what goes into making an episode. Behind the Scenes at Daria
